version_description: Explain why your version is different.

Unlike the other chords avalabile, I've timed the chords with their corresponding words - which is very helpful for the novice guitarist. Also I added the short tab about how to play like Tracy does in her recording.
Besonders bei diesem Song sind die Pausenzeiten beim Gesang. Diese sind anhand kleiner Striche markiert.

Building from the earlier versions, you will see this one has different chords in several places. The chord in parenthesis at the beginning of interludes means that the interlude phrasing begins at the end of the last chord of the previous line.
I couldn't find any tab or chord which was close enough for me, so here is my try with the fingerpicking pattern and the chords with the lyrics. Hope you'll enjoy this version as much as I do.

song_name: Chaos And Creation In The Backyard
